message: Really enjoyed your photos how stunning you looked in green . May I ask what you do for work ?.
Thanks so much Charles! I saw, you’ve been liking my content! I am a economics student and a hobby content creator. What about you? How do you change the world to a better place?
What countries have you been to? Which was your favorite one? Most important question: When are you coming to Bali? Would love to meet you in person! 😊

Good afternoon Kaila I hope you are having a. Super day so far, thank you for your questions so here goes. USA, Mexico, Grenada, Barbados, St Lucia, France, Spain, Portugal , Belgium, Holland, Germany ,Italy , Austria, Switzerland Czech Republic , Mauritius,Thailand, Malaysia , Hong Hong Singapore , Indonesia, New Zealand, Ireland. Now the hardest question you task me with ????. All the countries have enriched my life for so many reason the people, the history, etc . City. Singapore Country New Zealand Well I have to go to Thailand in December February Australia and New Zealand for cricket we have a World Cup competition in Late Feb ending 7th March so maybe after then ?. It would be lovely to meet this charming attractive young lady with a very sharpe mind too.

Darling thank you so much my goodness your last two pictures of you on the bed and the one above are nothing short of incredible beauty something very special and I am thrilled to have been lucky enough to view them darling.🥰❤️🥰❤️🙏🙏🙏
In the next few days will video call you if that is ok darling.
Hey! Thanks so much for the sweet words about the pics, darling. 😊 I'm still deep in my village project here in Bali, so video calls are a bit hectic right now. How's your day treating you?
